   <guid isPermaLink="true">http://www.dw.de/dw/episode/0,,15929448,00.html?maca=de-podcast_made-in-germany-2111-xml-mrss#15957978</guid>
   <title>„Just in Time“ – Logistik-Standort Deutschland</title>
